OL,3,CMother appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after baby girl fell from height
OL,6,FA mother has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering her 18-day-old daughter
OL,8,Fafter the baby fell from a residential
OL,9,Fproperty.
OL,11,FZahira Byjaouane, 43, was not asked to
OL,12,Fenter a plea at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Monday and spoke
OL,14,Fonly to confirm her name, date of
OL,15,Fbirth and address during the minutes-
OL,16,Flong hearing.
OL,18,FShe waved to loved ones in the public
OL,19,Fgallery as she entered and left the
OL,20,Fdock of the court.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
