CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773770757
OL,3,CMother appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after baby girl fell from height
OL,6,FHer case was deemed too serious to be
OL,7,Fdealt with at the magistrates' court
OL,8,Fand was sent to the Old Bailey where
OL,9,Fshe is due to appear on Wednesday.
OL,11,FJudge John Zani told her: "This case
OL,12,Fhas to be dealt with at the higher
OL,13,Fcourt and you will be appearing at the
OL,14,FCentral Criminal Court in two days'
OL,15,Ftime which is March 18.
OL,17,F"It is in custody by reason of the
OL,18,Fnature of the allegations. Bail does
OL,19,Fnot arise in this court."
