OL,3,CMother appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after baby girl fell from height
OL,6,FPolice officers attended Horseferry
OL,7,FRoad in Westminster, central London,
OL,8,Fon Saturday morning, following reports
OL,9,Fthat an infant had fallen from a
OL,10,Fheight, the Metropolitan Police said
OL,11,Fover the weekend.
OL,13,FThe baby girl was pronounced dead in
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FFlowers and a toy animal were left
OL,17,Fnear the Peabody Estate building on
OL,18,FSunday morning, where a police cordon
OL,19,Fhad been lifted.
